The PDF at WikiSource [[:File:Woodlands Cemetery, Philadelphia, Gwyn cemetery record for Section E 0033 N.5.pdf]] appears distorted when put into a thumb. However, if you view the PDF at WikiSource and click to enlarge, it appears at a normal aspect ratio: [http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/cb/Woodlands_Cemetery%2C_Philadelphia%2C_Gwyn_cemetery_record_for_Section_E_0033_N.5.pdf]

